<p><strong>Read it back.</strong> The trunk is at x = 3, z = 3, and stands from y = 1 to y = 2. The leaves fill x = 2 to 4 and z = 2 to 4, at y = 3 to y = 5.</p>
<p><strong>Now draw yours.</strong> Colour the squares.</p>
